entries.value: Welcome to the Accuracy Challenge...
we've acquired an empty building site for this game.
You'll be using the Poison Arrow in this one.
Use the weapon to poison the enemy worms
who are scattered about the landscape.
Poison them as fast as you can!
The faster the time, the better the score!
Step right up, step right up
time to test your crate collecting ability.
Gather up all the crates on the landscape...
as quickly as you can.
The Jet Pack Challenge.
You need to fly around the landscape
collecting crates as they appear.
The faster the time, the more respect you'll get!
Welcome back!
This time it's the Navigation Challenge.
Collect the first crate
then navigate your way around to collect the others.
Remember: Quicker is better!
Old Ladies love buildling sites...
in order to collect the target
quicker she collects the target the better you look!
well, they don't really.
Tons of concrete!
Some steel!
Got wood!
How could the old dears not like it?
Anyway, we've not brought our Old Lady here for fun
she's got a task to do
You need to steer her around the building site
"I am the genie of the lamp"
"You can collect the Teleport"
"and return to top to start again!"
"your wish is my command"
"Parachute Challenge? Sure thing!"
"I was thinking more a car or maybe a boat."
"You need to jump from the top of the landscape"
"collecting the first target you see"
"this will make the next target spawn, and so on."
"And when you reach the bottom..."
"Yes, do go on"
Welcome to the Icarus Potion Challenge.
Hope you've got a head for heights...
cos this involves some serious altitude!
You need to use the Icarus Potion...
in order to collect the crates...
which spawn in sequence.
You go get 'em!
Time for the Super Sheep Challenge!
Your skill with the Super Sheep will be tested to the max...
as you pilot the Super Sheep, collecting the crates.
This is the first one...
each time you collect one, another appears.
Feeling confident?
Hello there young worm...
and welcome to the Shotgun Challenge.
Don't worry about the dragon...
he's only there for eye candy...
it's the targets that should concern you!
No, really the dragon won't hurt you
Shoot the first target...
and the others will appear in sequence!
This time we have the Sniper Challenge!
Use your sight to zoom in on the landscape
and take out all the targets.
Go show 'em how to snipe like a proper worm!
Got It!
using the Parachute, collect as many targets as you can!
Quickly Jet Pack up to the next target!
Think you're pretty handy with the Parachute?
...we'll see.
Use the Parachute to make your way down the mountain...
collecting the targets as you go.
Targets equal time, remember that.
Nice Parachute skills!
Doing well, soldier. Keep on going!
Good work!  Now move across so you can see the other island..
Good work!  Now move back to the other island...
The targets will appear once you reach the second island, GO!
You're doing well, try to keep going!
Wow what skill! There's a new high-score on the horizon.
How on earth can a person possess such Shotgun-skill?
Welcome to the second Jet Pack Challenge...
Fly around the legendary logo, collecting targets as you go.
Targets equal time, the more time the higher the smugness!
"Camp Darkside"...
Once used as a prison to hold enemies of the Buffalo of Lies.
During the day they'd be locked in here,
in the evening they'd be forced to mine cheese!
These days it sits empty (apart from the odd, lost Mole)
so now we're about to put it to good use in a challenge!
"WOAH!"
...It seems our hero has bad memories of this place.
"EEEEEEEEEEEEK!"
Time to do a good job and lose those demons!
"GAME ON!"
Using the Super Sheep to collect the targets..
try and keep going for as long as possible!
Good luck!
Welcome to Super Sheep Challenge 2
Navigate your Super Sheep around the landscape,
collecting the targets as they appear.
Each target collected will increase your time.
The longer the challenge lasts, the better your ranking.
Welcome back...
In this challenge you'll have to negotiate the Port Stage!
Targets, if collected, still award time.
Don't be afraid of turning on your Super Sheep skill...
flying through this hanger is only part of it!
Find the optimum route through the challenge...
only then will you be able to manage a supreme time!
Ready?   "GAME ON!"
Hitting targets will add seconds to the clock..
only the best times will make the high score table..
so aim long, and aim true!
Nothing like a summers day in an English garden...
Flowers to smell...
More flowers to smell...
I HATE FLOWERS!
Let's just shoot things instead, that's more like it.
Let me guess, I gotta collect these targets?
Yes, Better get to it then...
Collect targets then Jet Pack back to the top..
Hmm, I love summer...
Never mind about that, there are targets to collect!
Welcome to the Wormfork Mine.
So do you think you can do that?
Excellent, well hop to it my annelid friend.
A lovely place I think you will agree.
Now we just need our worm.
There we go. Hello.
How are you today?
Excellent, so you ready to get started?
Brilliant. Ok see that crate over there?
All you have to do is collect it.
Then just carry on until you have collected all the crates.
Well done. That's all the crates collected.
Now you have loads of weapons.
All we need now is someone to use them on.
Ahh, this lot should do just fine.
They look harmless enough.
Oh come now, there's not that many.
Ok what if I did this?
Does that make you feel better?
Good. Now go kill!
Here is the battleground.
Nice isn't it?
Here are the enemy.
They're mocking you.
Don't stand for that.
Teach them a lesson they'll never forget!
And these are your enemies.
Nearly there!
Seek and destroy the enemy.
OK?
Then get to it!
Now, can you finish the job?
Hey, where are you?
Where are you hiding?
In here?
Ah, there you are.
What are you doing up there?
Anyway, you know what to do.
This Deathmatch should be fairly straightforward...
Let's meet the enemy shall we?
They don't look too tough do they?
There's four of them you know
Bring it on!
Welcome to another Deathmatch!
Maybe there are crates behind that volcano?
Hmmm...
And know your enemy...
You must take them out...
Before they get YOU!
Good luck!
Congratulations on the purchase of your new abode.
A renovators dream!
But whats this?
Where did these guys come from?
No, dont make friends.
Destroy them immediately!
Come on now, don't be scared...
Aww, it's not that bad!
I thought you liked Deathmatches?
No?
There's an enemy!
And another one!
You'll have to find where the rest are...
Good luck!
Welcome to Deathmatch 6!
This time things won't be so easy...
so you'll need to really turn on those skillz...
(yes, we meant skillz and not skills cos we're l33t)
It's not going to be THAT difficult!
Oh, come on you wimps!
You show these bullies what you're made of!
Welcome to another great Deathmatch!
Do your best to see off the enemy...
And be sure to make use of any crates you find!
Maybe there are some inside there?
Hmmm...
Hello there! Do you think you can take 'em?
Why are they laughing at you?
Hahaha! That's the spirit!
It's a gritty Deathmatch...
So you had better be at your best!
And get rid of this lot, pronto!
Surely you can take out these jokers?
HEY! You're not shaking are you?
You lying swine!
GO FOR IT!
Deathmatch 9 is upon us...
These worms look up for a scrap!
Question is: Are you?
Take that as a "No"?
Ready to go, guys?
Then go kick some pink butt!
Hoorah!
This battle takes place across an old town...
Cowboy stylee!
Feel free to have a look around...
enjoy the sights.
But don't forget these guys!
That is why you're here of course...
someone needs to tidy up this town.
You've disturbed a grave..
now deal with the rest of his horde!
Looks like you've dealt with everyone!
You cannot kill Dracuworm like that!
You must use the Baseball Bat!!
..the undead CRAWL!!
..creepy!!!
..deal with that sucker!
Eek!!  Your buddy is ZOMBIFIED!!
Woah, that's too WEIRD!
An enemy comes back to life next turn!
You've defeated Dracuworm..
You have been charged with the task of killing Dracuworm..
although he may appear weak, he is difficult to kill.
Only one of your Worms has the ability to deal with this threat,
you must strike with Van Wormsing's Baseball Bat!
Only then will the curse of the land be lifted.
Mind your step however, evil is close at hand!
Don't say you haven't been warned!
The Enemy Get Airstrikes Next Turn!!
We're carrying too many supplies
...looks like we'll need to ditch the Utilities!
Deep in Ali Baboon territory...
"Get down there and bring all our stuff back."
"RIGHT NOW!"
"And be quick about it"
"Before the enemy spot us!"
"Aaaah yes!"
"What an amazing performance!"
"We snatched the jewels back"
"Right from under their noses. Tee hee!"
"Now what's the matter?"
*Whimper*
"Where are all the weapons and tools?"
"sorry guys!"
"Errrm, I'm afraid I dropped them."
You collected the weapons...
and took out the enemy!
